ANALYSIS OF MAIN TARGET IMAGE

There are two separate “buildings” in the scene:

• Left Structure (6 total blocks, arranged in 3 vertical “levels”):
  1) Ground‐level wedges on either side (both orange)  
  2) A vertical orange cylinder in the center, flanked mid‐height by two blue cubes  
  3) A single orange “roof” wedge resting on top of the cylinder  

• Right Structure (8 total blocks, stacked in 4 layers):
  1) Bottom layer: two cubes side by side (left green, right orange)  
  2) Second layer: two cubes side by side (left orange, right green)  
  3) Third layer: two cubes side by side (left yellow, right blue)  
  4) Top layer: two orange wedge blocks forming a pitched roof  

SELECTED BLOCKS FROM DICTIONARY

Left Structure (6 blocks total):
• 1 × Index 7  (vertical orange cylinder)  
• 2 × Index 6  (blue cubes in the needed orientation)  
• 1 × Index 9  (orange wedge for the top “roof”)  
• 1 × Index 13 (orange wedge for the bottom left)  
• 1 × Index 14 (orange wedge for the bottom right)  

Right Structure (8 blocks total):
• 2 × Index 2  (green cubes)  
• 2 × Index 3  (orange cubes)  
• 1 × Index 4  (yellow cube)  
• 1 × Index 1  (blue cube)  
• 1 × Index 11 (orange wedge for left half of roof)  
• 1 × Index 12 (orange wedge for right half of roof)  

ASSEMBLY ORDER

{
  Step1:  Move block with index 13  // bottom-left orange wedge (left structure)
  Step2:  Move block with index 14  // bottom-right orange wedge (left structure)
  Step3:  Move block with index 7   // vertical orange cylinder (left structure)
  Step4:  Move block with index 6   // blue cube (left structure)
  Step5:  Move block with index 6   // second blue cube (left structure)
  Step6:  Move block with index 9   // top orange wedge (left structure)
  Step7:  Move block with index 2   // bottom-left green cube (right structure)
  Step8:  Move block with index 3   // bottom-right orange cube (right structure)
  Step9:  Move block with index 3   // second-layer orange cube (right structure)
  Step10: Move block with index 2   // second-layer green cube (right structure)
  Step11: Move block with index 4   // third-layer yellow cube (right structure)
  Step12: Move block with index 1   // third-layer blue cube (right structure)
  Step13: Move block with index 11  // left roof wedge (right structure)
  Step14: Move block with index 12  // right roof wedge (right structure)
}
